2d:["$","ul","ul-4",{"children":["\n",["$","li","li-0",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Offshore Wind"}],": Fleets of AUVs autonomously mapping the seabed before turbine installation, and regularly inspecting submerged cables for degradation."]}],"\n",["$","li","li-1",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Deep-Sea Mining"}],": Autonomous crawlers mapping polymetallic nodule fields while avoiding sensitive benthic ecosystems."]}],"\n",["$","li","li-2",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Climate Monitoring"}],": Gliders that change their buoyancy to passively \"fly\" through the ocean column for years, measuring temperature gradients and salinity to feed global climate models."]}],"\n"]}]
